rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Through here is the venue for the
summit of nations.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0002
rows.name:
I must apologize, but entry is forbidden
to all but the official representatives of
each nation.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0003
rows.name: I guess this is as far as we go.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes... Kagutsuchi and I will proceed
to the summit.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0005
rows.name: I'm coming with you.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0006
rows.name: Who invited you, Turtle-chan?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0007
rows.name: 'Scuse me?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0008
rows.name:
In case you've forgotten, I'm a prince
of Luxuria. I'm perfectly qualified to
represent my nation here.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0009
rows.name: Oh, yeah. I always forget.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0010
rows.name:
What do I have to do to get
some respect around here, eh?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Sorry, sorry. It's just you're so...
approachable. For a prince.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0012
rows.name: Uh-huh. I'll leave it at that.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0013
rows.name:
And so are you, Hikari.
Remember?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0014
rows.name: I guess...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0015
rows.name:
I'm not sure I like it, but I suppose
I have to play my part in all this.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0016
rows.name:
Rex, you head back to our chambers
with the others and wait for us.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0017
rows.name: No problems!

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0018
rows.name: Hang on, who needs babysitting here?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0019
rows.name: You figure it out.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0020
rows.name: Right. Sure.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0021
rows.name: Be careful in there, OK, Hikari?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0022
rows.name:
Don't worry.
I'll handle this just fine.
